{"tid":1782380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"莱特希泽：中国承诺未来2年内增购2000亿美元美国产品","createTime":"2019-12-14T02:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T03:08:20.000Z","uid":293332,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9512a883886284e9ff12bd8c4d9890ba2fc26aaa","tid":1782380,"uid":293332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"据《华盛顿邮报》报道，莱特希泽在当天向记者表示，此次与中方达成的协议是在长期以来试图改进&ldquo;不公的&rdquo;美中贸易关系中，（美方）取得的第一个成就。他在于白宫相邻的艾森豪威尔执行办公大楼中说，&ldquo;这是非常，非常重要的向前一步&rdquo;。莱特希泽称，&ldquo;有些人（就这一协议）会说&lsquo;你没有作一些最困难问题的部分&rsquo;，这当然也属实。但你也可以很容易换个角度看说，最困难的部分就是达成第一个协议；这是最艰难的一步&rdquo;。他并补充说，&ldquo;北京承诺在未来两年购买额外的2000亿美元美国产品，这包括美国农产品、能源和制造业产品&rdquo;。他指出，其中包括从美国农民手中购买320亿美元农产品。莱特希泽称，这次达成的协议中包含对单项商品设定的购买数额，例如家禽、动物饲料等，而这些项目则并未被公之于众，原因是要避免其对大宗商品市场产生影响。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20191213-%E8%8E%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B8%8C%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%89%BF%E8%AF%BA%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A52%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%85%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B02000%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E9%A2%9D%E5%A4%96%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%2F20191213-%25E8%258E%25B1%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AF%25BA%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%259D%25A52%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2586%2585%25E8%25B4%25AD%25E4%25B9%25B02000%25E4%25BA%25BF%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E9%25A2%259D%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25BA%25A7%25E5%2593%2581&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=abe2d7b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20191213-%E8%8E%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B8%8C%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%89%BF%E8%AF%BA%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A52%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%85%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B02000%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E9%A2%9D%E5%A4%96%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81</a>"},{"pid":"c7aa922ba16afa61e32baa4c7dfb86ad7b25ade1","tid":1782380,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b620f9897e91b08290eeae480bcd95d47917a07","tid":1782380,"uid":200049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:09:05.000Z","msg":"同場加映： 中國承諾有雙普選 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e475927892f5a67645f4dd04cc3bc313446ef4","tid":1782380,"uid":105219,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"320億美元農產品？？？<br />\n<br />\n侵唔係要五百億，然後中共回覆畀到400億咩？？ 點解最後仲少咗㗎？？"},{"pid":"a5f842e32ce2cdf7713cf1d58497e0067cabf956","tid":1782380,"uid":302531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"中國特色的承諾-&gt;歷史文件"},{"pid":"b9730aea8da0a7cda5d1c2a3707cccf8d17ea68e","tid":1782380,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"又係WSJ放故<br />\n當事人有出黎咩"}]}